data.title: Cheer Up
data.meta_description:
Cheer Up by Soul Low, released 28 July 2017

1. Intro
2. Bad Set of Moods
3. Propose to Me
4. Chancin' It
5. Could Be Nothing
6. Waterslide
7. Sad Boy Freestyle
8. Our New Deal
9. JD & Me
10. Amputee
11. Cheer Up

"Cheer Up" is the third full length album by Soul Low
All songs written & performed by Soul Low
Soul Low is Sam Gehrke, Jake Balistrieri, Sean Hirthe, Charlie Celenza

Recorded & mixed at Shane Olivo Audio
Mastered by Carl Saff

Album photograph by Phillip J. Hoffmann
